{"tid":83690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求推介] 床頭讀書燈","createTime":"2017-01-17T02:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T04:34:26.000Z","uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2db326fa0c775c8fcb2ddbba4db39d5fc88da289","tid":83690,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:53:13.000Z","msg":"想要一款叉電/入電芯, 有得夾住係床頭板既閱讀燈<br />\n<br />\n我睇好多都一係要叉住電用, 一係要插濕電, 一係座枱<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有推介?"},{"pid":"8071331cdbfa99b097bc31cf2958217b02b941b6","tid":83690,"uid":46337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:01:04.000Z","msg":"我係名創優品買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平平地幾好用"},{"pid":"bd5c3261004635d979d190e75fca0be724c5014c","tid":83690,"uid":28728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係名創優品買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平平地幾好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾牌子"},{"pid":"57ffa49ed17f77b0756ab2b9de4255f13da21910","tid":83690,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係名創優品買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平平地幾好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾牌子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人垃垃圾圾, 用垃圾牌子都得架啦<br />\n<br />\n你個隻係咪叉電+有得夾? 幾錢左右?<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太光? 有啲燈做得唔好睇書有眩光, 反而睇唔清楚"},{"pid":"35d7d74044bceecfc7cd163a4a6506211843f5c6","tid":83690,"uid":46337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係名創優品買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平平地幾好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾牌子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人垃垃圾圾, 用垃圾牌子都得架啦<br />\n<br />\n你個隻係咪叉電+有得夾? 幾錢左右?<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太光? 有啲燈做得唔好睇書有眩光, 反而睇唔清楚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果隻係叉電，但我無買夾，佢有三段光比你教<br />\n佢宜加開到周街到係可以睇下<br />\n因為佢出左好多款，都係30-70$左右"}]}